line-height:150%;text-align:left;mso-line-height-alt:25.5px;"><p style=3D"m=
argin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">Now, Calvin Klein appears to be pivoting again =
under the leadership
<strong>Stefan Larsson</strong>, who joined parentco/owner PVH in 2019 and =
replaced longtime C.E.O. <strong>Manny Chirico</strong> two years later. La=
rsson, a 50-year-old Swede, made his name at H&amp;M at the height of the f=
ast-fashion revolution before moving to San Francisco, where he had a succe=
ssful run at Old Navy. In 2015, he was named C.E.O. of Ralph Lauren, where =
he was tasked with enacting a turnaround, but left after two years because =
of disagreements with the namesake over how to move
ahead. (His strategy was famously called the Way Forward Plan, but Ralph ev=
idently didn=E2=80=99t like how<em> forward </em>it was.)=C2=A0</p><p style=
=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bott=
om:0px;">Larsson may communicate in contemporary C.E.O. speak=E2=80=94when =
he got fired from Ralph Lauren, he went on a =E2=80=9Clearning journey,=E2=
=80=9D meeting with industry insiders the world over=E2=80=94but he has amb=
itions to inspire the consumer, more in the style of the old-school Europea=
n executives and the
<strong>Mickey</strong> <strong>Drexler</strong> variety merchants, who bel=
ieve<em> creativity </em>fuels commerce. (In fact, before Larsson got the P=
VH job, he interviewed to be Drexler=E2=80=99s successor at J.Crew.)=C2=A0<=
/p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;=
margin-bottom:0px;">Larsson has spent the past few years addressing PVH=E2=
=80=99s most obvious problems=E2=80=94making the businesses less reliant on=
 Macy=E2=80=99s by turning up direct-to-consumer sales and finding other mo=
des of
distribution, etcetera. More broadly, however, Larsson=E2=80=99s aim is to =
transform PVH from a private equity-style holdco, in the vein of VF Corp., =
into a strategic organization that houses and nurtures brands. (I wouldn=E2=
=80=99t be surprised to see PVH eventually acquire Michael Kors.)=C2=A0</p>=
